\id PHM
\ide  UTF-8
\h Filemoni 
\toc1 Filemoni 
\toc2 Filemoni 
\toc3 phm 
\mt1 Filemoni  
\c 1
\cl Undyango 1 
\p
\v 1 Paul nkongwaa wa Yiisu Kristi, nu lukolo Timoti hwa filemoni, mmanyani nu gane vetu nu mbomba mbombo baninie nufwe.  
\v 2 nu hu ng'ancha vetu Afia, nu hwa Arkipas usihri njetu, nu hu-pelela u-guhwaganita pavujenge waho.  
\v 3 Uluhungu luve huliyomwe nu inonchehecho ulwihuma hwa Nguruve Daada vetu nu Nswambe Yiisu Kristi.  
\v 4 Emiseke gyone nihosana u Nguruve. Nihohotambula mwu nyesayo njango.  
\v 5 Nepulike ulugano nu luhungu uluulenalyo mu Yiisu na avakilisti vone.  
\v 6 Nihohodova ukuta ulululandamano nu lugano iwenyo five nu hulutelela mbu-jnsi wa inongwa inonu ichili hulyofwe nu Kristi.  
\v 7 U-lwahova nevile nu luhekelo nu luhuvilo ndu gano lwako, hu numbula incha vakilisiti nzivile nchinuna chiwa nuve, lukolo.  
\v 8 Lwa hova, neleno wvujima vwoni mwa krisiti nihuhulagila uve ukuvomba ihevuwesya ukuvomba.  
\v 9 Ulwahova nongwa ya lugano, nihohosimelencha one ne Pau ne gogolo, na leno nelekangwa aji ya Yiisu Krisiti.  
\v 10 Nihohodova hu nwambango Onesmo, yuywa neng'olile pukongwa wango.  
\v 11 U lwahuva pavutengulilo salehwidihana nuve na yone, leno ihwedehana nuve na yone.  
\v 12 Nesuhile umwene uva nu munumbula yango-uhuvuya hulyove.  
\v 13 Nihuvela uhutale ajige pupaninie nune, ili ambombelage apyanile palyove, asehe vu nele pukongwa hu nongwa ija uvangeili.  
\v 14 Ulwahova sanenogilwe ukuvomba hyohyoni hesitatavuliwa nuve ne vombile ulwahuva hesikuli ehenu ehenonu ehesahevombike kwa huhomehumelencha, ulwahuva wanogilwe yove uhuvomba.  
\v 15 Ulwahuva ale patali nuve useke unsupi -yale evo puave nuve amanchova goni.  
\v 16 Alehe uhuva insuhiwa, ave igane hulyione, nu hulotelela kulovye, mwu mbele na kurudeva.  
\v 17 Inave vuhonolela one pu-kristi, umpokehe ndu alaleihomohela une.  
\v 18 ingave ukuvipiche ehenu hyohyoni, apange vuhodaya ehenu hyohyoni, udaye ehyo ukuhuma hulyone.  
\v 19 Unene Paul, nisimba ne kevoko kyango yune: one nelahohomba. Saninchora kulyove uhuta ulenukole mu mitamele kyaho gyioni.  
\v 20 Eena lukolo, indeke nupelele luhekelo lwa Nkundeva uhuhome hulyove: uguhovye untema gwango mwa krisiti.  
\v 21 Nengave nu lwedekopa luginio lwako, ihohosimbela vunelomanyile ulavomab nu kuhutelela hu fila ifyonikudova.  
\v 22 Useke gugugwa utesanie eheyumba hya avagenji hya hufikile une, ulwahuva nihovela uhugendela inyesayo nchaho nihuhugendela unseke usupi.  
\v 23 Epafra, onkongwa njango mwa Yiisu Kristi nihohopania.  
\v 24 Ndu umuivomba Malika, Aristarko, Dema, Luka ava vombambombo nune.  
\v 25 Ulusayo lwa Nswambe U Yiisu Kristi luve paninie ne numbula yako. Amen.   